<plot>In a little village in Tuscany, during 1939, all the people is looking forward for Mussolini official visit. The Duce will inaugurate the village's primary school. Unexspectedly the corpse of a baby is found as a result of a murder. At this point almost all the inhabitants will do their best to delay the visit of Mussolini and to hide the crime.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?028889</url></doc>
